          |                 
          li Officiant
          |                 
          li Death Doula
          |                 
          li Estate Services
      |             
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col-desktop
        ul.ui-reset-ul
          li Florist
          |                 
          li Caskets and Urns
          |                 
          li Body Donation Organization
      |             
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col-desktop
        ul.ui-reset-ul
          li Cemetery
          |                 
          li Funeral Consumers Alliance
          |                 
          li Organ and Tissue Donation
  |       
  section.mdl-layout.ui-padding-bottom-md
    .mdl-grid.mdl-typography--text-center(data-layout='size-lg')
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
        h2 Benieuwd naar de voordelen voor uw onderneming?
        |
        a.ui-padding-horizontal-xl.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent(href='contact.html') Contact Us
